        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-center gap-6 max-w-5xl mx-auto">
            <a href="https://lin.ee/Xs8Orp2" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="flex-1 bg-green-500 hover:bg-green-600 text-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-lg transition-transform hover:scale-105 flex flex-col items-center justify-center">
                <div class="text-2xl font-bold mb-2">LINEで見積もり</div>
                <div class="text-sm">写真を送るだけでスムーズ対応</div>
